üìå Project Overview
This project presents an end-to-end Amazon Sales Analysis using Power BI, aimed at converting raw transactional sales data into actionable business insights.
The dashboard helps stakeholders understand:
‚Ä¢	Sales performance
‚Ä¢	Product demand patterns
‚Ä¢	Fulfillment efficiency
‚Ä¢	Customer behavior
‚Ä¢	Regional revenue contribution
The analysis is designed for business decision-making, performance monitoring, and strategy planning.
________________________________________
