1. Interactive Power BI Dashboard
‚Ä¢	High-level KPI cards for quick insights
‚Ä¢	Sales, orders, and AOV trends
‚Ä¢	Dynamic slicers for category, fulfillment, and date filtering
‚Ä¢	Drill-down enabled visuals
2. Multi-Page Analytical Views
‚Ä¢	Sales Overview
