üìå KPIs Used
‚Ä¢	Total Revenue
‚Ä¢	Total Orders
‚Ä¢	Average Order Value (AOV)
‚Ä¢	Total Quantity Sold
‚Ä¢	Cancelled Orders
‚Ä¢	Cancellation Rate (%)
