‚Ä¢	B2B vs B2C Revenue Contribution
________________________________________
üîç Key Insights
‚Ä¢	T-Shirts contribute the highest revenue among all product categories
‚Ä¢	Medium and Large sizes account for the majority of sales volume
‚Ä¢	Amazon-fulfilled orders outperform merchant fulfillment
‚Ä¢	Metro & Tier-1 cities (Bengaluru, Mumbai, Delhi) dominate revenue share
‚Ä¢	Cancellation rate remains relatively low, indicating strong fulfillment efficiency
________________________________________
‚úÖ Business Recommendations
‚Ä¢	Increase inventory focus on high-performing categories and sizes
‚Ä¢	Strengthen logistics operations in top-revenue cities
‚Ä¢	Introduce targeted offers to increase Average Order Value
‚Ä¢	Monitor cancellation reasons to further optimize fulfillment
