üöÄ How to Use This Project
1.	Download the Power BI (.pbix) file from GitHub
2.	Open it in Power BI Desktop
3.	Use slicers to filter data by category, date, fulfillment, and region
4.	Explore individual dashboard pages for detailed insights
5.	Modify or extend the analysis as per business needs
